subject: Automobile Racing
organizations: National Assn of Stock Car Auto Racing
lead_paragraph: Jimmie Johnson, the two-time reigning Nascar Sprint Cup champion, gave Rick Hendrick’s powerhouse team its first victory of the year Saturday night in the Subway Fresh Fit 500.
